<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="faqs-section" style="max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <div class="faqs">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        1. How to book a slot?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        You can book a parking slot in real-time through our dashboard after logging in.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        2. What payment methods are accepted?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        We accept UPI, credit/debit cards, and mobile wallets.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        3. Can I cancel my booking?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes, bookings can be canceled from your dashboard before the booked time.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        4. Is the parking system secure?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes, we have CCTV monitoring and secure access systems in place.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        5. Can I book slots in advance?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes, you can reserve parking slots ahead of time using our booking system.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        6. Are there any extra charges for cancellations?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        No, cancellations made before the booking time are free of charge.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">
        7. What if I face issues with booking?
        <span class="triangle">&#9656;</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Contact us via the contact page or phone, and our support team will assist you promptly.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="/js/faqAccordion.js"></script>

